Package: aiR
Date: 2014-11-07
Title: Areal interpolation and geographic aggregation
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Adam", "Slez", email = "aslez@virginia.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides basic tools for areal interpolation and
    geographic aggregation.  Interpolation tools are not currently available.
    Aggregation is based on the identification of common geographies or
    "clusters," as per the method outlined by Slez, O'Connell, and Curtis
    (2014).
Depends: R (>= 3.1.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Imports: igraph, dplyr, tidyr, rgeos
Packaged: 2015-01-23 18:09:48 UTC; Adam
Author: Adam Slez [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Adam Slez <aslez@virginia.edu>
